^B@2hondo717: Now, as to moe's takeout double  Here are my guidelines for takeout doubles. they are my opinion, not absolutes.
First of all, you should have an opening hand.  moe is just a smidgen short, as he does not have an opening hand by the rule of 20. Further, I tend to subtract one point for 4-3-3-3. |
